(1, 'Should India Boycott Chinese Products', 'Ashish', 'International', '2020-07-20', '&lt;hr style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 3pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Nationwide Campaign&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; Started to boycott Chinese goods after the military aggression along the Line of Actual Control (LAC) in Ladakh resulting in the sacrifice of 20 soldiers of the Indian Army.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;But before concluding to any decision, we must consider the following pros and cons.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table class=&quot;table table-bordered&quot;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ffffff&quot; face=&quot;Verdana&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Why Chinese Products Should Be Banned&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Verdana; font-size: 14.4px; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Why Chinese Products Should Not be Banned&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Security Threat&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Intelligence Agencies have flagged 52 applications that are reportedly linked to China and may possess security and privacy threats.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Georgia; color: rgb(61, 66, 57); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Apps such as UC Browser and TikTok are no longer tool-based products, but content players in India.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;[Opinion] India Following The Concept Of Banning Country-Specific Applications.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;China has always been known to build walls. In a historic context, the Great Wall of China and in a modern context, the Great &ldquo;Firewall&rdquo; of China. By banning Country-specific applications, India is also following the same concept.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&ldquo;Aatmanirbhar Bharat Abhiyaan&rdquo; - Initiative by Prime Minister of India&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Boycotting Chinese products may lead to opportunities for local products in India due to an increase in demand. This will also be helpful for startups to grow their business easily in the Indian market.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Lack Of Skilled Workforce And Infrastructure.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Indian youth has a disparity between classroom knowledge and practical applications. This has resulted in a shortage of relevant skills. India is also lacking in infrastructures like semiconductor manufacturing or electronic equipment manufacturing companies.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Increase In GDP.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;If we somehow manage to overcome the challenges in the establishment of manufacturing industries, India can export finished goods rather than raw materials, resulting in an increase in GDP.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Sanctions on India by the World Trade Organization.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Both India and China are members of WTO and boycotting the products of China means India may suffer some sanctions on import and export from WTO. Also, export from India to China is dispensable (like raw materials) which can easily be replaced by any other country while import from China to India is indispensable (like electronic products) which are cheap.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;China supports Pakistan&rsquo;s stands.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Most of the time China supports Pakistan&rsquo;s interests which are in opposition to India&rsquo;s interests. For instance, China and Pakistan both opposed India in being a member of the Nuclear Supplier Group. Boycotting China products could be our strategic foreign policy to overcome this pressure.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Arab Countries supporting Pakistan.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Some Arab countries like Saudi Arab, Iran, etc have always supported Pakistan on many fronts. Are we ready to use the same strategy for these countries and boycotting the import of crude oil and gas?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div dir=&quot;ltr&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px; text-align: center; margin-left: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span arial=&quot;&quot; black&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div dir=&quot;ltr&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px; margin-left: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-a1a3b785-7fff-fdac-2e62-00a3e5ead8aa&quot;&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', '04:15:09 PM', 'Should-India-Boycott-Chinese-Products', '&lt;div data-height=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.kialo.com/should-india-boycott-chinese-products-38210&quot;&gt;Should India Boycott Chinese Products?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &mdash; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.kialo.com/&quot;&gt;kialo.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;script async src=\'https://www.kialo.com/assets/frontend-buildtag-stable-660/static/js/embedded-kialo.min.js\' charset=\'utf-8\'&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 'https://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/intel-agencies-red-flag-use-of-52-mobile-apps-with-links-to-china-complete-list/story-B50Slf39aSnVOrCcS92l1N.html\r\n\r\nhttps://pib.gov.in/PressReleaseIframePage.aspx?PRID=1623514\r\n\r\nhttps://www.skillreporter.com/2020/02/editorial/india-is-facing-acute-shortage-of-skilled-workforce/\r\n\r\nhttps://indianexpress.com/article/explained/india-china-trade-ban-explained-6465949/\r\n\r\nhttps://thediplomat.com/2020/06/the-limits-of-indias-urge-to-boycott-chinese-brands/', 'Should India Boycott Chinese Products Edited second time', 'Nationwide Campaign Started to boycott Chinese goods after the military aggression along the Line of Actual Control (LAC) in Ladakh resulting in the sacrifice of 20 soldiers of the \r\nIndian Army.\r\n\r\nBut before concluding to any decision, we must consider the following pros and cons.', 'India, China, Boycott, 2020, Made in India', 'Post'),
(2, 'Lockdown Report Card: Pass or Fail', 'Ashish', 'Covid19', '2020-06-23', '&lt;hr style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 3pt; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;India has already gone through 4 phases of nationwide lockdown due to COVID 19 pandemic and currently in an unlocking phase. We have seen the consequences of the lockdown, both positive and negative, but before concluding to any result let us clear out the facts.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table class=&quot;table table-bordered&quot;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Verdana; font-size: 14.4px; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Accomplishments&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Verdana; font-size: 14.4px; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Failures&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Reduction in Growth Rate.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The COVID 19 growth rate has reduced &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;from 24.3% in the pre-lockdown phase to 3.8% in unlock 1.0 phase&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Failed in Flattening the Curve.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The main motto of the lockdown has not yet achieved and India is now getting the highest number of patients each day.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Improved Environmental Conditions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Positive changes have been shown in environmental conditions not only in India but all around the world.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Impact on the Indian Economy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(32, 33, 34); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;On 26 May, CRISIL announced that there will be India\'s worst recession since independence. SBI research estimates a contraction of over 40% in the GDP in Q1 FY21.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(32, 33, 34); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Restraining the pandemic up to the cities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The situation would be more dangerous if the pandemic enters the villages of India having insufficient medical facilities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Migration of working class.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The unplanned migration resulted in huge chaos for the working class.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Development of Infrastructure.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Lockdown provided the required time to develop the infrastructure to fight COVD 19.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Lack of facilities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Non-COVID 19 patients faced a difficult situation due to the lack of transportation and medical facilities.&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial Black&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-f404b9d0-7fff-c6a2-5bc9-baaf361b9544&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.656;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '03:41:38 PM', 'Lockdown-Report-Card-Pass-or-Fail', '&lt;div data-height=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.kialo.com/lockdown-report-card-pass-or-fail-38677&quot;&gt;Lockdown Report Card: Pass or Fail?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &mdash; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.kialo.com/&quot;&gt;kialo.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;script async src=\'https://www.kialo.com/assets/frontend-buildtag-stable-660/static/js/embedded-kialo.min.js\' charset=\'utf-8\'&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 'https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/economy/indicators/india-facing-its-worst-recession-in-current-fiscal-says-crisil/articleshow/76004775.cms?from=mdr', 'Lockdown Repost Card Pass or Fail edit', 'India has already gone through 4 phases of nationwide lockdown due to COVID 19 pandemic and currently in an unlocking phase. We have seen the consequences of the lockdown, \r\n\r\n\r\nboth positive and negative, but before concluding to any result let us clear out the facts.\r\n\r\n', 'Covid-19, Corona, Lockdown, India', 'Post'),
(3, 'The War of Donations', 'Ashish', 'Politics', '2020-07-05', '&lt;hr style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 3pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.38; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-dff08766-7fff-19e3-1f7a-d7b53c934635&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Since the last 2 weeks, a new debate between the ruling party and the opposition party has emerged on the topic of the donation f&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;rom foreign sources. Let us see the facts presented by both sides.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table class=&quot;table table-bordered&quot;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Verdana; font-size: 14.4px; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;BJP\'s Claim&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Verdana; font-size: 14.4px; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Congress\' Claim&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Donation received by Rajiv Gandhi Foundation from the Chinese embassy in 2005-06 was used for conducting studies that were not in the national interest.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Rs 1.45 crore donation from the Chinese embassy was used by the Rajiv Gandhi Foundation (RGF) for the welfare of disabled persons and research on Indo-China relations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Congress had diverted Prime Minister National Relief Fund (PMNRF) to the Rajiv Gandhi Foundation. Sonia Gandhi as Congress president was on the board of the PMNRF and also headed the RGF.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The fund was utilised for tsunami relief work carried out on behalf of the Rajiv Gandhi Foundation in Andaman and Nicobar islands in 2005.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;India will not accept financial assistance from the governments of the other nations to the &ldquo;PM-Cares Fund&rdquo; to deal with the COVID-19 crisis, but it will remain open to receiving donations from the overseas citizens of the country, foreign individuals and non-government entities to the trust.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;PM Cares Fund received donations from Chinese companies like TikTok, Xiaomi, Huawei, OnePlus amidst the Indo-China border tension.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.38; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Foreign Contribution (Regulation) Act&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-87ecfb1e-7fff-7242-eb9b-b5a70e76ab6a&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; color:=&quot;&quot; rgb(0,=&quot;&quot; 0,=&quot;&quot; 0);=&quot;&quot; background-color:=&quot;&quot; transparent;=&quot;&quot; font-variant-numeric:=&quot;&quot; normal;=&quot;&quot; font-variant-east-asian:=&quot;&quot; vertical-align:=&quot;&quot; baseline;=&quot;&quot; white-space:=&quot;&quot; pre-wrap;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;It was illegal for an Indian political party or NGO to receive funding from foreign sources (including a company that has &ldquo;more than one-half of the nominal value of its share capital held&rdquo; by &ldquo;corporations incorporated in a foreign country or territory&rdquo;) until 2016.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; color:=&quot;&quot; rgb(0,=&quot;&quot; 0,=&quot;&quot; 0);=&quot;&quot; background-color:=&quot;&quot; transparent;=&quot;&quot; font-variant-numeric:=&quot;&quot; normal;=&quot;&quot; font-variant-east-asian:=&quot;&quot; vertical-align:=&quot;&quot; baseline;=&quot;&quot; white-space:=&quot;&quot; pre-wrap;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;In 2014, the Delhi High Court had found both the Congress and the BJP had violated this rule.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; color:=&quot;&quot; rgb(0,=&quot;&quot; 0,=&quot;&quot; 0);=&quot;&quot; background-color:=&quot;&quot; transparent;=&quot;&quot; font-variant-numeric:=&quot;&quot; normal;=&quot;&quot; font-variant-east-asian:=&quot;&quot; vertical-align:=&quot;&quot; baseline;=&quot;&quot; white-space:=&quot;&quot; pre-wrap;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;The definition of &ldquo;foreign source&rdquo; was changed by amending the FCRA. Now, as long as a company had foreign investment limits as per Indian law, it was by law an &ldquo;Indian company&rdquo;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14.4px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-9632d0e2-7fff-a656-0fad-94ed98078b2d&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '04:03:26 PM', 'The-War-of-Donations', '&lt;div data-height=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.kialo.com/the-war-of-donation-between-bjp-and-congress-38678&quot;&gt;The War of Donation between BJP and Congress&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &mdash; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.kialo.com/&quot;&gt;kialo.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;script async src=\'https://www.kialo.com/assets/frontend-buildtag-stable-660/static/js/embedded-kialo.min.js\' charset=\'utf-8\'&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 'https://www.indiatoday.in/india/story/congress-dismisses-bjp-allegations-says-donation-from-chinese-embassy-pmnrf-used-for-welfare-purpose-1693233-2020-06-27\r\n\r\nhttps://www.indiatoday.in/india/story/nadda-congress-pmnrf-donation-rgf-opposition-randeep-surjewala-bjp-deception-1692950-2020-06-26\r\n\r\nhttps://www.deccanherald.com/national/pm-cares-fund-not-to-accept-financial-assistance-from-foreign-governments-820541.html\r\n\r\nhttps://thewire.in/politics/fact-check-have-chinese-companies-really-donated-to-the-pm-cares-fund\r\n\r\nhttps://scroll.in/article/966243/china-is-killing-indian-soldiers-why-are-indian-parties-allowed-to-take-funds-from-chinese-firms\r\n\r\nhttps://www.thehindu.com/news/national/fcra-amendment-in-finance-bill/article22636668.ece\r\n', 'the war of donation edit', 'Since the last 2 weeks, a new debate between the ruling party and the opposition party has emerged on the topic of the donation from foreign sources. Let us see the facts presented by both sides.', 'Congress, BJP, Donations, ', 'Post');
