rrent government into a tough situation proving majority in the state assembly.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-1944a8c8-7fff-f3a3-1cbb-322e02f2ef06&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-weight:normal;&quot; id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-3048d126-7fff-9a87-d4a7-67734d7674da&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Ashok Gehlot &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;claimed that&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;102 MLA&rsquo;s are in support of the current Congress-led government in Rajasthan resulting in a majority.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-weight:normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;While the future of the current government is highly dependent on the response of Sachin Pilot in the next two days, let us see what options are available to Pilot and Gehlot.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-weight:normal;&quot; id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-c8dc4504-7fff-2473-837e-d95f45ce8dd1&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;&quot;&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Pilot returning to Congress on the same post of Deputy CM. Congress, after failing to hold the government in Karnataka and Madhya Pradesh, may have gained experience of handling these situations. But Pilot is not in a mood to choose this option.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-weight:normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;&quot; start=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Pilot joining BJP along with the MLAs of the rebel group. This will be resulting in falling of the current Congress-led government. This would be a major setback for Congress after the Karnataka and Madhya Pradesh situation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-weight:normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;&quot; start=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Pilot getting back with Congress on a promise of Cheif Minister post. This will save the current Congress-led government. But for this to happen, Congress will have to face resistance from a senior political leader (Gehlot) and his supporters in the party.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-weight:normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;&quot; start=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Pilot returning to Congress satisfying only with the post of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#202122;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;President of the Rajasthan Pradesh Congress Committee. This will result in the marginalisation of Pilot and his supporters in the future.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-weight:normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;&quot; start=&quot;5&quot;&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:decimal;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#202122;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#202122;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Pilot leaving Congress party and starting a new political party in Rajasthan along with his supporters. The consequences of this option will be seen in future elections in Rajasthan.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;&quot; start=&quot;6&quot;&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:decimal;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#202122;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#202122;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Pilot quitting Congress party as well as politics. This will be the last option anyone can think of. After claiming that he is not joining BJP and apparently not in a mood of getting confronted with Gehlot, this will the most honourable decision taken by him in this situation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-9150360d-7fff-dd97-3bca-a61b28576f06&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Whatsoever be the decision taken by Sachin Pilot, it is clear that Congress will have to face a difficult situation in future. It is time to decide whether the party wants to give way to youth political leaders like Sachin Pilot or continue with the experience of the veteran leaders like Ashok Gehlot.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; face=&quot;Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-d39881e8-7fff-e6c8-5f12-6a1f4ed8ca18&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '04:00:45 PM', 'Game-of-Power-in-Rajasthan', '&lt;div data-height=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.kialo.com/game-of-power-in-rajasthan-39039&quot;&gt;Game of Power in Rajasthan&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &mdash; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.kialo.com/&quot;&gt;kialo.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;script async src=\'https://www.kialo.com/assets/frontend-buildtag-stable-663/static/js/embedded-kialo.min.js\' charset=\'utf-8\'&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 'https://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/i-m-not-joining-bjp-says-sachin-pilot/story-ll9EmizHTKq0vCZeCJ6byJ.html\r\n\r\nhttps://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/bjp-demands-cbi-probe-into-rajasthan-phone-tap/story-YsxCwXZ3gam7oPxfQKIajI.html\r\n\r\nhttps://www.indiatoday.in/news-analysis/story/rajasthan-political-crisis-ashok-gehlot-sachin-pilot-scenarios-1699955-2020-07-13\r\n \r\n', 'game of power in Rajasthan', 'The political crisis started with friction between CM Ashok Gehlot and Deputy CM Sachin Pilot have taken dramatic turns in the past few days. After denial of the possibilities of joining BJP by Pilot and the call tapping incident done by Congress, the question remains the same: â€œ What is the future of political power in Rajasthan? â€. \r\n', 'Rajasthan, Congress, BJP, Pilot, Gehlot', 'Post'),
(5, 'Kargil War: Lessons learned by both countries.', 'Ashish', 'International', '2020-07-26', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:3pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:26pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-05091fe2-7fff-ac82-f046-7733f52f3bf5&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:3pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;India is celebrating 21st &ldquo;Kargil Vijay Diwas&rdquo; on 26 July 2020 and remembering the courage, determination and sacrifice of the brave soldiers of Indian armed forces who fought to protect the country in 1999.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-weight:normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The Kargil war was started&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; with the infiltration of both Pakistani troops and terrorists into Indian territory. Based on information from local shepherds, the Indian Army was able to ascertain the points of incursion and launch &quot;Operation Vijay&quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; India eventually won the war, but t&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;his victory came at a high price. The official death toll on the Indian side was 527, while that on the Pakistani side was between 357 and 453. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;It was one of the few instances when war was fought between two nuclear states.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-weight:normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;While the diplomatic relations of both countries are getting from bad to worse, here are some lessons learned by both countries from this war:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-weight:normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot; color=&quot;#ffffff&quot;&gt; What did India learn? &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-weight:normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;&quot;&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The international support provided to India on the Kashmir issue cannot be taken for granted. India must maintain a degree of responsibility and seeking peace in the Kashmir valley to ensure the international as well as regional support.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-weight:normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;&quot; start=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;India cannot neglect the Kashmir issue in hopes of gradual atrophy. This issue requires a high level of commitment and responses from government&rsquo;s side. The Abolition of Article 370 in October 2019 was one such response by the Indian government, keeping in mind the strategic misuse of Article 370 by Pakistan in making Kashmir an International Issue.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-weight:normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;&quot; start=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;India must be prepared for any recklessness caused along the LOC (Line Of Control), either by the Pakistani military or some terrorist groups.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-weight:normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;&quot; start=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;India must more aggressively counter Pakistani threats by investing in more technologically advanced military and intelligence equipment.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-weight:normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ffffff&quot;&gt; What did Pakistan learn? &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-weight:normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;&quot;&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Kargil war appears to have a failure for Pakistan in the eyes of the world. Operations like Kargil are not an effective means to resolve a dispute and seeking stability in the region.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-weight:normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;&quot; start=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Any attempt from Pakistan to forcefully redraw the Line Of Control can lead to a full-fledged war between the two nuclear states, resulting in instability within both countries.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-weight:normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;&quot; start=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The nuclear capability of Pakistan cannot completely rule out a conventional conflict. India knows to handle international pressure during any conflict in South Asia by using a strategy (though not official) of speedy military victory while remaining below the nuclear threshold.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-weight:normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;&quot; start=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Pakistan believes to have few or no diplomatic options, to bring India on the negotiating table,&amp;nbsp; other than the continued prosecution of sub-conventional conflict in Kashmir and perhaps elsewhere in India.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-05091fe2-7fff-ac82-f046-7733f52f3bf5&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h6 style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot; segoe=&quot;&quot; ui&quot;,=&quot;&quot; roboto,=&quot;&quot; &quot;helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue&quot;,=&quot;&quot; arial,=&quot;&quot; sans-serif,=&quot;&quot; &quot;apple=&quot;&quot; color=&quot;&quot; emoji&quot;,=&quot;&quot; &quot;segoe=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; symbol&quot;,=&quot;&quot; &quot;noto=&quot;&quot; emoji&quot;;=&quot;&quot; color:=&quot;&quot; rgb(128,=&quot;&quot; 128,=&quot;&quot; 128);=&quot;&quot; text-align:=&quot;&quot; center;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/h6&gt;', '04:12:16 PM', 'Kargil-War-Lessons-learned-by-both-countries-', '&lt;div data-height=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.kialo.com/can-peace-be-attained-in-kashmir-through-a-war-39140&quot;&gt;Can peace be attained in Kashmir through a War?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &mdash; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.kialo.com/&quot;&gt;kialo.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;script async src=\'https://www.kialo.com/assets/frontend-buildtag-stable-665/static/js/embedded-kialo.min.js\' charset=\'utf-8\'&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 'https://www.hindustantimes.com/opinion/lessons-pakistan-army-learnt-from-kargil-and-one-it-did-not/story-aLG79EGzCF7GrtXU061gqI.html\r\n\r\nhttps://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-49234708\r\n\r\nhttps://www.outlookindia.com/magazine/story/the-lessons-of-kargil/207909\r\n\r\nhttps://www.rand.org/pubs/monograph_reports/MR1450.html\r\n', 'kargil war lessons learned edited aa', 'India is celebrating 21st â€œKargil Vijay Diwasâ€ on 26 July 2020 and remembering the courage, determination and sacrifice of the brave soldiers of Indian armed forces who fought to protect the country in 1999. Let us see what India and Pakistan learned from this war?\r\n', 'India, Kargil, Pakistan, War, 1999', 'Post');
