(6, 'The National Security Law vs Hong Kong', 'Navneet & Ashish', 'International', '2020-07-29', '&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 36pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 36pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 36pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 36pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 36pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 36pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 36pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h1 style=&quot;text-align: center; margin-left: 36pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-7624d796-7fff-44e3-31d7-7d044a6e0e76&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; margin-left: 36pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5 style=&quot;text-align: left; margin-left: 36pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-7624d796-7fff-44e3-31d7-7d044a6e0e76&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;What has happened?&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;h5 style=&quot;text-align: left; margin-left: 36pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-7624d796-7fff-44e3-31d7-7d044a6e0e76&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: left; margin-left: 36pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;China has passed the National\r\nSecurity Law for Hong Kong to safeguard its internal security.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: left; margin-left: 36pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;font-family:&quot; arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:arial;mso-ansi-language:=&quot;&quot; en;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:hi&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;The move has been condemned\r\nall over the world and developing high tensions in Hong Kong.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: left; margin-left: 36pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;font-family:&quot; arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:arial;mso-ansi-language:=&quot;&quot; en;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:hi&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;Pro-democratic protests\r\ntaking all over Hong Kong\'s streets, Beijing responded with brutality resulting\r\nin the detention of thousands of activists.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; margin-left: 36pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5 style=&quot;margin-left: 36pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;Key Events You Need to Know&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; margin-left: 36pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo3&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;1842&lt;/b&gt; - &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;In the 1st Opium War China was defeated\r\nby the British Empire which resulted in cede of Hong Kong island to Britain.&lt;b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo3&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;1898 &lt;/b&gt;- &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;Britain negotiated with China and the\r\nlease over Hong Kong was set up for 99 years i.e. till 1997.&lt;b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;\r\n&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;1984&lt;/b&gt; - &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;UK &amp;amp; China signed the Sino -\r\nBritish joint declaration outlining their plan for Hong Kong.&lt;b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo5&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;1st July 1997 &lt;/b&gt;- &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;Hong Kong was given back to\r\nChina but on terms of recognition as Special Autonomous Region and the\r\nresidents must be allowed to enjoy their administrative system i.e. 1 country 2\r\nsystems for the next 50 years i.e. till 2047.&lt;b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;\r\n&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;2019&lt;/b&gt; - &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;Protests broke out over proposed extradition\r\nlaw which violates the 1 country 2 system.&lt;b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;28th May 2020&lt;/b&gt; - &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;On this day Beijing decided\r\nHong Kong\'s faith by passing the National Security Law. This move has faced\r\nmassive opposition all over the world. Many see this as the &lt;b&gt;DEATH OF HONG KONG.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5 style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;WHAT IS NATIONAL SECURITY LAW &amp;amp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;WHY PEOPLE ARE AFRAID OF IT?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; The new law\'s key\r\nprovisions include that:&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;Crimes of secession, subversion,\r\nterrorism and collusion with foreign forces are punishable by a maximum\r\nsentence of life in prison.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;Damaging public transport\r\nfacilities can be considered terrorism.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;Those found guilty will not be\r\nallowed to stand for public office.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;Companies can be fined if\r\nconvicted under the law.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;Beijing will establish a new\r\nsecurity office in Hong Kong, with its law enforcement personnel - neither of\r\nwhich would come under the local authority\'s jurisdiction.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;This office can send some cases to\r\nbe tried in mainland China - but Beijing has said it will only have that power\r\nover a &quot;tiny number&quot; of cases.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;Besides, Hong Kong will have to establish\r\nits national security commission to enforce the laws, with a Beijing-appointed\r\nadviser.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;Hong Kong\'s chief executive will\r\nhave the power to appoint judges to hear national security cases, raising fears\r\nabout judicial autonomy.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;Importantly, Beijing will have\r\npower over how the law should be interpreted, not any Hong Kong judicial or\r\npolicy body. If the law conflicts with any Hong Kong law, the Beijing law takes\r\npriority.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;Some trials will be heard behind\r\nclosed doors.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;People suspected of breaking the\r\nlaw can be wire-tapped and put under surveillance.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;Management of foreign\r\nnon-governmental organizations and news agencies will be strengthened.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;The law will also apply to\r\nnon-permanent residents and people &quot; from outside [Hong Kong] ... who are\r\nnot permanent residents of Hong Kong &quot;.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&ldquo;It is clear that the law will\r\nhave a severe impact on freedom of expression, if not personal security, on the\r\npeople of Hong Kong,&quot; Professor Johannes Chan, a legal scholar at The University of Hong Kong.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5 style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;CHINA\'S CONCERN&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;Last year, protests over an\r\nextradition law turned violent and evolved into a broader anti-China and\r\npro-democracy movement.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;China doesn\'t want to see that\r\nhappen again.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;China\'s concern over its internal security is alright but\r\nshould it achieve security by curbing the freedom of its people or shall Hong\r\nKong accepts the law in name of safeguarding the country, the question arises.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-67bfc515-7fff-29e2-59d8-6beb9d783c37&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;h5 style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 128, 128); text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial&quot; color=&quot;#424242&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: Tahoma;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 36pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '04:10:08 PM', 'The-National-Security-Law-vs-Hong-Kong', '', 'https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-52765838\r\n\r\nhttps://www.nytimes.com/2020/06/30/world/asia/hong-kong-security-law-explain.html\r\n', 'NSL vs Hongkong', 'China has passed the National Security Law for Hong Kong to safeguard its internal security. The move has been condemned all over the world and developing high tensions in Hong Kong. Let us see the complete story behind the issue.', 'China, Hong Kong, National, Security, Law, 2020', 'Post');
