(14, 'Centre clarifies after Finance Ministry circular, no ban on recruitment for Government jobs', 'Sumit', 'General', '2020-09-06', '&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Finance minister :&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;â— The Dept. of Expenditure circular dated 04 Sept 2020 deals with internal procedure for creation of posts and does NOT in any way affect or curtail recruitment.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;â— There is no restriction or ban on filling up posts in Government of India. Normal &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;recruitment&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt; through govt agencies like Staff Selection Commission, &lt;font color=&quot;#FF0000&quot;&gt;UPSC, Railway Recruitment Board, etc &lt;/font&gt;will continue as usual without any restrictions.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Congress leader :&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;â— Rahul Gandhi tweeted Covid is just an excuse, the government\'s plan is to free government offices of all permanent staff, steal the youth\'s future and propel his own friends forward.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;â— The Congress on Saturday demanded that the Centre withdraw its circular calling for a freeze on the creation of new posts, and urged it to create more vacancies while filling the existing ones in the wake of the alleged rise in unemployment.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '11:58:46 AM', 'Centre-clarifies-after-Finance-Ministry-circular-no-ban-on-recruitment-for-Government-jobs', '', 'https://zeenews.india.com/india/no-ban-on-recruitment-for-government-jobs-centre-clarifies-after-row-over-finance-ministry-circular-2307799.html\r\nhttps://www.timesnownews.com/', 'Centre clarifies after Finance Ministry circular no ban on recruitment for Government jobs', '', 'Finance, Ministry, Government Jobs, Job,Jobs,gov,Rahul Gandhi, Nirmala Sithraman', 'Report'),
(15, 'Can Suresh Raina go back for IPL?', 'Sumit', 'General', '2020-09-06', '&lt;p&gt;Suresh Raina: Raina told a leading magazine,that when &lt;font style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot; color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;CSK&lt;/font&gt; bio bubble is not safe how does one take chance. I have family with two little kids.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;A BCCI official has said that if Suresh Raina returned to India because of depression, he won\'t be allowed to return to play &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(247, 198, 206);&quot;&gt;IPL 2020.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;On Friday, Raina told a news agency: &quot;It was a personal reason and I had to come back for my family&quot;, referring to the unfortunate and violent incident in Pathankot that took a huge toll on his family. Raina denied that he had returned because there was a rift with CSK skipper MS Dhoni.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If he came back because of depression, then it\'s a mental issue,BCCI official said.&lt;/p&gt;', '04:19:16 PM', 'Can-Suresh-Raina-go-back-for-IPL-', '', '', 'Suresh Raina', '', 'India, IPL, CSK, Suresh, Raina, 2020, Sports', 'Report'),
(16, 'Is the guru-shishya parampara still relevant in Indian classical music?', 'Sumit', 'General', '2020-09-06', '&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;Traditions:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Several minutes before the fire broke out before the death of &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 231, 156);&quot;&gt;Pandit Jasraj&lt;/font&gt; in Vile Parle crematorium, his students who had gathered to pay their last respects sang a hymn.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Sung in raag Sindhu Bhairavi, the melodic framework that embodies sorrow and separation, the bhajan wasn&rsquo;t just a tribute to a great musician&rsquo;s life.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Among them was 34-year-old Ankita Joshi, who had been the late musician&rsquo;s student for 22 years. She had spent 17 of those years living in Jasraj&rsquo;s home, imbibing her lessons in the ancient guru-shishya format.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;The New Trend:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;It&rsquo;s this conflict between the demands of tradition and contemporary society that a recent film and a web-series The Discipline have explored, in this a classical singer is challenged by contemporary life as he follows tradition of his guru.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;In the web series, a new feature film by Chaitanya Tamhane, a classical vocalist is challenged by contemporary life as he follows the tradition and teachings of his guru.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;A similar theme of tradition versus modernity plays out in Bandish Bandits, a web-series, According to one of the show&rsquo;s creators, Amritpal Singh Bindra, Bandish Bandits grew out of a discussion with actor-singer Namit Das, ghazal singer Chandan Dass&rsquo;s son.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '07:38:29 PM', 'Is-the-guru-shishya-parampara-still-relevant-in-Indian-classical-music-', '', 'https://indianexpress.com/article/express-sunday-eye/indian-classical-music-guru-shishya-6584626/', 'Guru shishya', '', 'India, Classical, Music, Culture, Pandit Jasraj', 'Report'),
(17, 'The talks deadlock between UK & European Union.', 'Ashish', 'General', '2020-09-07', '&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;United Kingdom&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;PM &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 214, 99);&quot;&gt;Boris Johnson&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;said that UK will quit Brexit talks if no deal by October 15.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;PM Johnson said that Britain could walk away from the talks within weeks and insisting that a no-deal exit would be a &ldquo;good outcome for the UK&rdquo;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;An agreement would only be possible if EU negotiators are prepared to &ldquo;rethink their current positions&rdquo;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;European Union:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;The European Union, in turn, accuses Britain of failing to negotiate seriously.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 214, 99);&quot;&gt;Michel Barnier&lt;/font&gt; said last week he was &ldquo;worried and disappointed&rdquo; by the lack of progress and said the UK had not &ldquo;engaged constructively&rdquo;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&quot;We would prefer a deal, but a deal on the basis of our mandate,&rdquo; he told France Inter radio. &ldquo;There is room for action, but the whole package, including the fishing package, needs to be taken up in order to avoid a &lsquo;no deal.\'&quot; - French Foreign Minister &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 214, 99);&quot;&gt;Le Drian&lt;/font&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', '12:39:58 PM', 'The-talks-deadlock-between-UK-European-Union-', '', 'https://m.hindustantimes.com/world-news/johnson-says-uk-will-quit-brexit-talks-if-no-deal-by-oct-15/story-m7Pk5fYrgGIXdTfySz8cGK_amp.html', 'Deadlock UK and EU', '', 'International, United Kingdom, Britain, European Union, Brexit', 'Report'),
(18, 'Bihar government\'s decision: A helping hand or a discriminational move?', 'Vinay', 'General', '2020-09-07', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;State Government:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;The Bihar government has taken a decision to provide a government job to one family member of any SC/ST who gets killed.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;The state government is to frame rules to give a government job to the next of kin of any SC/ST person killed in Bihar. CM Nitish Kumar on Friday directed scheduled caste and scheduled tribe (SC/ST) welfare secretary Prem Kumar Meena to get the rules framed at the earliest.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Opposition:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;The RJD leader on Saturday said the move, &ldquo;was like encouraging murder of SC/ST people&rdquo;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;After the announcement of job by Bihar government for SC/ST person, RDJ leader said Why shouldn&rsquo;t jobs be given to kin of people of OBC, or general category, who are killed,this is like encouraging murder of SC/ST people,&rdquo; Mr. Tejashwi Yadav said, while addressing media persons in Patna.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;', '03:03:06 PM', 'Bihar-government-s-decision-A-helping-hand-or-a-discriminational-move-', '', '', 'Bihar Decision', '', 'India, Bihar, Nitish Kumar, RJD, caste', 'Report'),
(19, 'Does actress Kangana Ranaut need security?', 'Vinay', 'General', '2020-09-07', '&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Actress :&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;The actress kangana said she feared Mumbai Police more than the &quot;movie mafia&quot;, and would prefer security either from Himachal Pradesh or the Centre.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Officials said the Himachal Pradesh government has requested the Central government to provide security to Ranaut through a paramilitary force.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;BJP leader Ram Kadam recently asked the Shiv Sena-led Maharashtra government to provide police protection to Ranaut since &quot;she wanted to expose the Bollywood drug nexus&quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Shiv Sena:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Shiv Sena leader Sanjay Raut purportedly said, &quot;We kindly request her not to come to Mumbai. This is nothing but an insult to Mumbai Police.&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Raut had on Friday urged the Maharashtra government to take action against people defaming the city police.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;He also asked Ranaut to tour the PoK first to see the situation prevailing there.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;', '04:08:43 PM', 'Does-actress-Kangana-Ranaut-need-security-', '', '', 'Kangana Ranaut security', '', 'Kangana Ranaut, BJP, Shiv Sena', 'Report'),
(20, 'Re-Ignition of Fire observed on MT New Diamond', 'Sumit', 'General', '2020-09-08', '&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Indian Navy :&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Indian Navy on Monday said that a re-ignition of the fire was observed on the starboard side of the oil tanker &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;MT New Diamond&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Indian Navy said that fire-fighting and boundary cooling efforts were intensified to bring the fire under control.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Indian Navy said in a tweet that additional assets, salvage personnel &amp;amp; FF equipment also enroute.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Indian Coast guard :&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Indian Coast guard said that the fire onboard oil tanker MT New Diamond off Sri Lanka coast has been douse, adding that cooling of the ship was in progress.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;The Indian Coast guard had been engaged in fire fighting and pollution response operation for MT New Diamond.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Indian Coast guard Ships Sujay, Shaurya, Sarang and Pollution Response Vessel Samudra Paheredar are continuously engaged in fire fighting operation on rotation using specialised external fire fighting systems.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', '01:07:35 PM', 'Re-Ignition-of-Fire-observed-on-MT-New-Diamond', '', 'https://zeenews.india.com/india/re-ignition-of-fire-observed-on-mt-new-diamond-says-indian-navy-2308253.html', 'Re ignition of fire', '', 'India, Sri Lanka, MT New Diamond, oil, fire, 2020, Indian Oil Corporation', 'Report'),
(21, 'Mob beats Murder-accused in front of UP police', 'Sumit', 'General', '2020-09-08', '&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Eyewitness\' statement:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Eyewitness said that, the accused was ready to surrender before the police, but the mob continued beating him, and finally resulted in his death.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The Murder-accused has been beaten to death by a violent Mob in Kushinagar district, Uttar Pradesh.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Asthe mob brutally attacked the accused, police officers were present in the scene, but they failed to protect the life of the man who should have been under their custody.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;According to Eyewitness, The man\'s head appeared to have been bashed in and the ground was splattered with blood by the time the crowd was done with him.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Police:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Officer said that, a police team followed him to the terrace but the man escaped and was caught by a crowd, which set upon him. Soon, someone called the police and a team arrived.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;According to the Police, the man was from Gorakhpur and rode a scooty into the village, looking for a teacher, Sudhir Kumar Singh, claiming to be his brother\'s friend.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;As soon as he saw Singh, he took out his father\'s gun and killed the teacher, It is not known yet why.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;According to the SP Vinod Kumar Mishra, the police have started an investigation to unravel the mysteries surrounding the entire incident.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;', '05:43:59 PM', 'Mob-beats-Murder-accused-in-front-of-UP-police', '', 'https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.ndtv.com/india-news/kushinagar-man-accused-of-murder-beaten-to-death-in-presence-of-cops-in-uttar-pradesh-2291591%3famp=1&amp;akamai-rum=off\r\n', 'Mob beats murder accused', '', 'India, Uttar Pradesh, Kushinagar, Police, Crime', 'Report'),
(22, 'Rhea Chakraborty arrested by NCB in drugs conspiracy related to SSR case.', 'Sumit', 'General', '2020-09-08', '&lt;h5&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;NCB&lt;/font&gt; :&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;â— The actress &lt;font color=&quot;#ce0000&quot;&gt;Rhea Chakraborty &lt;/font&gt;will undergo medical tests including coronavirus examination before the NCB produces her before the court.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;â— NCB source said, will not demand Rhea&rsquo;s custodial interrogation as she has already been questioned at length. This means she now goes to jail.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;â— The source added that she evaded answering some direct questions related to procurement of drugs for Rajput, or delivery of drugs to her parents&rsquo; house.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;â— The NCB arrested Rhea under the following Sections of the NDPS (Narcotic Drugs and Psychotropic Substances) Act 1985:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;â–  Section 27 (a): Punishment for financing illicit traffic and harbouring offenders.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;â–  Section 20 (b): Punishment for contravention in relation to cannabis plant and cannabis.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;â–  Section 8 (c): Prohibition of certain operations. No person shall produce, manufacture, possess, sell, purchase, transport, warehouse, use, consume, import inter-State, export inter-State, import into India, export from India or tranship any narcotic drug or psychotropic substance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;â–  Section 28: Punishment for attempts to commit offences.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;â–  Section 29: Punishment for abetment and criminal conspiracy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Rhea Chakraborty&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt; :&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;â— Rhea\'s lawyer Satish Maneshinde described her arrest as a &ldquo;travesty of justice&rdquo;. &ldquo;Three central agencies (ED, CBI, NCB) hounding a single woman, just because she was in love with a drug addict.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;â— Rhea told the NCB officials during the questioning that she used to smoke drugs-filled cigarette with late star Sushant Singh Rajput. Rhea also claimed that Sushant was consuming drugs since 2016.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;â— Rhea in her complaint claimed that&amp;nbsp; persons including Sushant\'s Sister Priyanka Singh, Meetu Singh, Delhi-based doctors Tarun Kumar and others hatched a conspiracy and obtained false prescription on the letterhead of a government hospital for banned medicines &amp;amp; administered the same to the actor without supervising doses &amp;amp; quantity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '08:07:49 PM', 'Rhea-Chakraborty-arrested-by-NCB-in-drugs-conspiracy-related-to-SSR-case-', '', 'https://www.indiatvnews.com/entertainment/news/breaking-rhea-chakraborty-detained-by-ncb-drugs-nexus-sushant-singh-rajput-death-case-645737\r\nhttps://zeenews.india.com/people/rhea-chakraborty-arrested-by-ncb-in-drugs-conspiracy-related-to-sushant-singh-rajput-case-2308357.html\r\nhttps://theprint.in/india/ncb-arrests-rhea-chakraborty-for-drug-abuse-in-sushant-singh-rajput-death-case/498330/', 'Rhea Chakraborty arrested by NCB in drugs conspiracy related to SSR case', '', 'Rhea chakraborty, Sushant Singh case,CBI,Mumbai,ssr', 'Report'),
(23, 'Tamil Nadu Government told Centre that they wouldn\'t apply 3-language formula ', 'Sumit', 'General', '2020-09-09', '&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Tamil Nadu:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;The Tamil Nadu government has made it clear to the Centre that it wouldn\'t introduce the &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;three-language policy&lt;/font&gt; and continue with the two-language formula in the state.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Tamil Nadu has always followed the two-language formula, which has been a success. The state government has already taken a decision to &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 198, 156);&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;continue with the two-language policy&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt; in future.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;The minister also opposed the proposal to conduct entrance exams for UG courses by National Testing Agency, saying the move would discourage rural students.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;What NEP recommended:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;The NEP recommends that all Students will learn three languages in their school under the \'Formula\', at least &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 198, 156);&quot;&gt;two of the three languages should be native to India&lt;/font&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;If a student in Mumbai is learning Marathi and English, he/she will have to choose to learn another Indian language.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;The choice of languages learnt will depend on the state and the students. However, it is mandatory for at least two of the three languages to be native to the country &ndash; one of which is most likely to be the local/regional language.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;', '12:48:12 PM', 'Tamil-Nadu-Government-told-Centre-that-they-wouldn-t-apply-3-language-formula-', '', 'https://www.thequint.com/news/education/new-education-policy-medium-of-instruction-mother-tongue-faq\r\n\r\nhttps://m.timesofindia.com/india/wont-apply-3-language-formula-tamil-nadu-tells-centre/amp_articleshow/77988162.cms', 'Three language policy', '', 'India, Tamil Nadu, National Education Policy, 2020, Language', 'Report'),
(24, 'PUBG Mobile will no longer be developed by Tencent in India', 'Vinay', 'General', '2020-09-09', '&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Indian Government:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Indian government banned &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;PUBG&lt;/span&gt; mobile which has largest market in india,nearly one-fourth of the game user. After announcement of the ban, &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;Tencent&lt;/font&gt; lost nearly &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 198, 156);&quot;&gt;$34 billion of its value in 2 days&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Some applications were blocked by the Government on the grounds of prejudice to sovereignty and integrity of India and security of state and public order.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;According to Tanu banerjee, disengagement with Tencent may not be of any particular benefit for PUBG Mobile.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;National security considerations make overturning of the ban under 69A of the IT Act rather difficult. However, with a change of ownership, the South Korean owner will have a better chance for set up committee in India.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;PUBG Corporation:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;It hopes to work hand-in-hand with the Indian government to find a solution that will allow gamers to once again drop into the battlegrounds.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;PUBG mobile is not giving hopes in India, PUBG Corporation,&amp;nbsp; trying to make original PUBG game&lt;u&gt;,&lt;/u&gt; is &quot;hoping to work hand in hand with Indian government to find a Solution&quot;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The company has decided to shed it\'s &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 198, 156);&quot;&gt;\'chinese tag\' &lt;/font&gt;for the indian market and will not allow China based Tencent games to be it\'s franchise in India.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 0.9rem;&quot;&gt;Responding to the ban, PUBG Corporation has made the decision to no longer authorise the PUBG franchise to Tencent game in India.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;', '04:22:57 PM', 'PUBG-Mobile-will-no-longer-be-developed-by-Tencent-in-India', '', 'https://www.gadgetsnow.com/tech-news/pubg-mobile-to-shed-its-chinese-tag-in-india/articleshow/77990891.cms\r\n\r\nhttps://www.google.com/amp/s/www.businessinsider.in/tech/apps/news/pubg-mobile-will-no-longer-be-developed-by-tencent-in-india/amp_articleshow/77993013.cms', 'PUBG mobile not by Tencent', '', 'India, China, Gaming, PUBG, Tencent, ban', 'Report'),
(25, 'BMC\'s act a contempt of High Court?', 'Vinay', 'General', '2020-09-09', '&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Bombay Municipal Corporation:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;The BMC on Wednesday demolished&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;&ldquo;illegal alterations&rdquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt; at the Bandra bungalow of Ranaut, a civic official said.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;BMC started demolishing Kangan Ranaut\'s Mumbai office for alleged unauthorized modifications/extensions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;BMC had put a new notice on the actress\'s office in Bandra on Wednesday morning stating that many alterations were carried out on the premises without due permissions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;BMC said that the&nbsp; fresh notice pasted outside the actor&rsquo;s office today said that the civic body was not satisfied with the actor&rsquo;s response.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Kangana Ranaut:&nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;She said that there is no illegal construction in her house, also &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;High Court&lt;/font&gt; has banned any demolitions in Covid till September 30.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Kangana\'s lawyer had written to BMC, it has rejected her appeal claiming that the work done on the property is &quot;beyond approved plan&quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Kangana moved to the High Court against the demolition drive of her Bandra office.&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Kangana Ranaut hit back at Maharashtra chief minister &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;Uddhav Thackeray&lt;/font&gt;, your ego will be destroyed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;', '08:58:26 AM', 'BMC-s-act-a-contempt-of-High-Court-', '', 'https://www.google.com/amp/s/indianexpress.com/article/cities/mumbai/kangana-ranauts-mumbai-office-demolition-live-updates-bmc-6588945/lite/\r\nhttps://www.google.com/amp/s/www.indiatvnews.com/amp/entertainment/celebrities/kangana-ranaut-vs-bmc-live-updates-mumbai-office-demolition-actress-lands-mumbai-heavy-security-breaking-news-648323', 'BMC act a contempt of High Court', '', 'India, Maharashtra, BMC, Kangana Ranaut, High Court', 'Report'),
(26, 'Fire Destroys Most of Europeâ€™s Largest Refugee Camp on Greek Island of Lesbos', 'Sumit', 'General', '2020-09-10', '&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Greek Government:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Greek government officials have speculated that the fire may have been set intentionally.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Stelios Petsas, a government spokesman, told Greek television on Wednesday that the fire&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt; &ldquo;wasn&rsquo;t accidental,&rdquo;&lt;/font&gt; and may have been set by camp residents.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;He said, there was a very widespread protest front by the refugees and migrants when they were asked to go into quarantine.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Aid Workers:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Aid workers said it began sometime after dark on Tuesday following protests by residents over recent coronavirus restrictions and quickly spread because of &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 231, 206);&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;high winds and the explosion&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt; of gas canisters.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Nearly the entire camp, the largest in Greece, was on fire, including an olive grove outside the walls of the main compound where many slept in tents. People were seen escaping the camp, carrying their belongings.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Aid groups have long criticised the cramped and unsanitary living conditions at Moria, which make physical distancing and basic hygiene measures impossible to implement.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;', '01:41:33 PM', 'Fire-Destroys-Most-of-Europe-s-Largest-Refugee-Camp-on-Greek-Island-of-Lesbos', '', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2020/09/09/world/europe/fire-refugee-camp-lesbos-moria.html\r\nhttps://www.aljazeera.com/amp/news/2020/09/moria-ablaze-hundreds-forced-flee-overcrowded-camp-greece-200909035949757.html', 'Fire Destroys Most of Europe Largest Refugee Camp on Greek Island of Lesbos', '', 'Europe, Greek, fire, refugees, camp', 'Report'),
(27, 'Oxford-AstraZeneca vaccine trails paused.', 'Vinay', 'General', '2020-09-10', '&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Oxford University:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Trials of &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;Oxford-AstraZeneca&rsquo;s&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt; Covid-19 vaccine have been paused, reportedly after severe adverse reaction in a participant in England.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Global pharma major AstraZeneca announced late on Tuesday evening that it was putting a halt on ongoing clinical trials for a coronavirus vaccine it is developing in collaboration with Oxford University.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Oxford University said that it was a &ldquo;voluntary&rdquo; and &ldquo;routine action&rdquo; that happens &ldquo;whenever there is a potentially unexplained illness in one of the trials&rdquo;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Oxford-AstraZeneca candidate vaccine is undergoing phase 3 trail in the US, Brazil, South Africa and same vaccine that was cleared for combine phase 2 and 3 trail in India.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Serum Institute of India:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&ldquo;As far as Indian trials are concerned,we have no issue. We are follow the direction of DCGI\'s and we have not ask to stop trail and we follow the all standard protocols.&quot;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;India&rsquo;s central drug regulator Wednesday issued a notice to Pune-based Serum Institute of India (SII), asking why the firm hadn&rsquo;t informed it about the &ldquo;reported serious adverse events&rdquo; that led its UK partner AstraZeneca.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Drugs Controller General of India &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;V G Somani&lt;/font&gt; sought to know why permission granted for Phase 2 and 3 trials shouldn&rsquo;t be suspended till patient safety is established.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The notice came even as Serum Institute CEO &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;Adar Poonawalla&lt;/font&gt; said Phase 2 and 3 trials would continue and also said &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 156, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&ldquo;The vaccine is completely safe&quot;.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;', '04:15:10 PM', 'Oxford-AstraZeneca-vaccine-trails-paused-', '', '', 'Oxford AstraZeneca vaccine trails paused', '', 'Covid-19, Corona, vaccine, Oxford, AstraZeneca, SII Pune', 'Report'),
(28, 'Jaishankar and Wang to meet today as troops mass along LAC', 'Sumit', 'General', '2020-09-10', '&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Chinese Foreign Ministry :&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Chinese Foreign Minister &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;Wang Yi&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt; said that tensions have surged in Ladakh where 5000-7000 Chinese soldiers backed by tanks and artillery.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;The Chinese have been reluctant to &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 231, 206);&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;complete troop disengagement&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt; on the Pangong Tso north bank and at Gogra Post.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Chinese Soldiers said that shots were fired Monday evening, a first at the LAC in 45 years, 30-40 Chinese troops continue to be 200-300 metres away from Indian positions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Indian Foreign Ministry :&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Indian Foreign Minister &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;S Jaishankar&lt;/font&gt; said that the Chinese have been trying to &ldquo;dislodge&rdquo; Indian troops from their new positions at multiple locations, almost daily.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Excellent talks that reflect our Special and Privileged Strategic Partnership. Value our exchanges on the international situation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;A senior Army officer said that at the brigade commander level talks, India has let China know about certain&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 231, 206);&quot;&gt; &ldquo;red lines&rdquo;&lt;/font&gt; that their troops should not cross.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;', '09:26:49 PM', 'Jaishankar-and-Wang-to-meet-today-as-troops-mass-along-LAC', '', 'https://indianexpress.com/article/india/at-ric-meet-in-moscow-jaishankar-and-wang-to-meet-today-as-troops-mass-along-lac-6589872/', 'Jaishankar and Wang to meet today as troops mass along LAC', '', 'India, China, LAC, Army, Border, Meeting', 'Report'),
(29, 'Life ban on Politicians convicted for heinous offences?', 'Sumit', 'General', '2020-09-11', '&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Supreme Court :&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;The Supreme court asked the centre to respond to a new prayer of a &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 156, 0);&quot;&gt;life ban on politicians&lt;/font&gt; convicted of &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 156, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;heinous offence&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt; from contest elections.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Senior advocate&amp;nbsp;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;Vikas Singh&lt;/font&gt; said there was a long list of serious crimes in which conviction of a public servant led to his disqualification from holding a government job for his lifetime but there is no any list for convicted politicians. &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 231, 206);&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&ldquo;Why can&rsquo;t the same yardstick be applied to politicians who, under the Representation of People Act, get away lightly by getting debarred from contesting elections for a period of six years after serving the jail term?&rdquo;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt; he asked.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;A bench of Justices N V Ramana, Surya Kant and Hrishikesh Roy sought the Centre&rsquo;s response in six weeks on the petition, in which the court had sought reports from all high courts on the cases pending trial against sitting and former legislators.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Supreme Court\'s bench grant two days time to the remaining HCs to provide requisite information of pending cases and their stages excluding HCs of Karnataka, Madhya Pradesh, Tamil Nadu, Delhi, Jharkhand and Gauhati.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Representation of The Peoples Act:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 156, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;Section 8 (1)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;: A person convicted for promoting enmity between different groups, rape, terrorist acts, insulting the national flag, etc should disqualified for six years on punishment.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 156, 0);&quot;&gt;Section 8 (2):&lt;/font&gt; A person is convicted for hoarding, dowry offenses etc., if he is sentenced to a minimum of 6 months for the offense he is disqualified. The bar continues for 6 years following his release from prison.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 156, 0);&quot;&gt;Section 8 (3)&lt;/font&gt;: A person is convicted of disqualification for any other offense if he is sentenced to imprisonment of not less than two years, disqualification continues for six years after issue.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 156, 0);&quot;&gt;Section 8 (4):&lt;/font&gt; Protects MPs and MLAs from disqualification under the above provisions, if they file an appeal within three months, they continue as members of the House until the term is over or the appeal is decided can keep first.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;', '04:21:50 PM', 'Life-ban-on-Politicians-convicted-for-heinous-offences-', '', '', 'Life ban on Politicians convicted for heinous offences', '', 'India, Politics, Democracy, Representation of the People act, Supreme Court, Government', 'Report'),
(30, 'Is BJP using Sushant Singh Rajput for Bihar election?', 'Vinay', 'General', '2020-09-11', '&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Shiv Sena :&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Shiv Sena has accused the BJP of &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 198, 156);&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;politicizing&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt; Sushant Singh Rajput&rsquo;s death case for the upcoming elections in Bihar saying votes of a particular caste matters.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Shiv Sena\'s &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;Saamana&lt;/font&gt; alleged that BJP was politicizing Sushant Singh Rajput death case for the upcoming Bihar polls.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Sena said if the itch of politics has subsided, then politicians should pay attention to the issues of national interest, national security, and the livelihood of the people.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Political analyst &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;Hemant Desai &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;also opined that post SSR probe, the Sena had now closed all doors on BJP and the party would sharpen its attack on the Opposition and vice versa.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;BJP :&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;BJP state spokesperson said we were only focusing on taking up people\'s issues and the role of strong Opposition. We are not thinking about future relations and we are expressing  people &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 198, 156);&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;sentiment&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt; over SSR probe.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The proxy war between the Shiv Sena and the Bharatiya Janata Party (BJP) over the Sushant Singh Rajput probe.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The BJP&rsquo;s shadow attack on Sena scion and tourism minister &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;Aaditya Thackeray&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt; in the case and now Centre&rsquo;s backing of actor Kangana Ranaut has rankled and irked the Sena.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;A senior state BJP leader also said that the way SSR probe narrative had been played out dealt a death knell on any future alliance with the Sena.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;', '09:30:33 PM', 'Is-BJP-using-Sushant-Singh-Rajput-for-Bihar-election-', '', 'https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.timesnownews.com/amp/india/article/for-votes-of-a-particular-caste-shiv-sena-accuses-bjp-of-politicizing-ssrs-death-for-upcoming-bihar-polls/650869\r\nhttps://www.google.com/amp/s/m.hindustantimes.com/cities/bjp-shiv-sena-fight-gets-fiercer-over-sushant-singh-rajput-s-death-probe/story-lePvi6K4Pm36OppDpomPfI_amp.html', 'Is BJP using SSR for Bihar election', '', 'India, Bihar, BJP, Sushant Singh Rajput, elections', 'Report');
INSERT INTO `post` (`id`, `title`, `author`, `category`, `date`, `blog`, `upload_time`, `post_url`, `code`, `source`, `image_name`, `brief`, `tags`, `type`) VALUES
(31, 'Farmers protest over the Three Central Ordinances', 'Ashish', 'General', '2020-09-12', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;The Three Ordinances:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;The Farmers&rsquo; Produce Trade and Commerce (Promotion and Facilitation) Ordinance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Essential Commodities (Amendment) Ordinance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Farmers (Empowerment and Protection) Agreement on Price Assurance and Farm Services Ordinance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Centre\'s motive:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;The ordinance merely provides for &ldquo;trade areas&rdquo; outside the physical boundaries of APMC mandis.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Union Agriculture Minister &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;Narendra Singh Tomar&lt;/font&gt; has said that the ordinance would serve as an &ldquo;additional marketing channel&rdquo; for farmers, even as the APMCs &ldquo;will continue to function&rdquo;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;The freedom of choice to sell outside the regulated mandis should help farmers realise better prices for their produce.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;It &ldquo;will motivate APMCs to improve their efficiency of operations substantially to serve the farmers better&rdquo;. The APMCs can levy mandi fees and other charges as before, but these will be only in respect of transactions happening within the physical boundary of their principal marketing yards or sub-yards.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Farmers\' opposition:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;The dismantling of the monopoly of APMCs is a precursor to ending the existing system of government grain procurement at assured minimum support prices (MSP).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Farmer leaders contend that the true intent of the latest reforms is to implement the recommendations of the &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;Shanta Kumar&lt;/font&gt;-headed High Level Committee on Restructuring of Food Corporation of India (FCI).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;This panel, which submitted its report in 2015, had called for FCI handing over all procurement operations in Punjab, Haryana, MP, Chhattisgarh, Odisha and Andhra Pradesh to state government agencies.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&ldquo;The committee wanted that the Centre exit procurement and leave everything to the states. Where do they have the money for procuring and stocking so much grain? This&hellip; is only meant as an exit strategy for the Centre,&rdquo; alleged &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;Jagmohan Singh&lt;/font&gt; (BKU)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '01:35:00 PM', 'Farmers-protest-over-the-Three-Central-Ordinances', '', 'https://indianexpress.com/article/explained/three-ordinances-protest-why-are-haryana-farmers-angry-6592559/lite/', 'Farmers protest over the Three Central Ordinances', '', 'India, Haryana, Punjab, Farmers, Government, ordinance', 'Report'),
(32, 'Microsoft unhappy with Apple\'s new rules', 'Vinay', 'General', '2020-09-12', '&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Apple :&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Apple said that game streaming services, such as &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;Google Stadia&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt; and &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;Microsoft xCloud&lt;/font&gt;, are explicitly permitted with some conditions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Apple revised its App Store guidelines on Friday ahead of the release of iOS 14, the latest version of the iPhone operating system, which is expected later this month.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;All rules have come under intense investigation in recent weeks from app makers who argue iPhone maker has too much control.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Apple\'s rules mean that if a streaming game service has 100 games, then each of those games will need an &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 231, 206);&quot;&gt;individual App Store listing&lt;/font&gt; as well as a developer relationship with Apple.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Microsoft :&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Microsoft clearly remains unhappy with Apple&rsquo;s new rules and Xbox gamers that have iOS devices look set to be devoid of xCloud platform.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Microsoft xCloud is a platform that will allow users to play and access Xbox games via streaming.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Microsoft isn&rsquo;t impressed. &ldquo;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 231, 206);&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;This remains a bad experience for customers,&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&rdquo; says a Microsoft spokesperson in a statement to The Verge.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Microsoft said &ldquo;Gamers want to jump directly into a game from their curated catalog within one app just like they do with movies or songs, and not be forced to download over 100 apps to play individual games&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;', '08:43:28 PM', 'Microsoft-unhappy-with-Apple-s-new-rules', '', 'https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.cnbc.com/amp/2020/09/11/apple-app-store-new-rules-will-affect-google-stadia-microsoft-xcloud.html', 'Microsoft unhappy with Apple new rules.', '', 'Microsoft, Apple, Google, ', 'Report'),
(33, 'Protest in Pakistan after gang rape of woman in front of children on highway', 'Sumit', 'General', '2020-09-12', '&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Anger among People:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Protests have broken out in cities across Pakistan after a police chief investigating the gang rape of a woman on a major national highway on Thursday, appeared to &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 231, 206);&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;blame the victim &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;for travelling late at night without a male companion.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;In her statement to the police, the woman said she was waiting for help to arrive when a group of men smashed her window, dragged her out of the car and raped her in front of her children in a nearby field.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Hundreds took to the streets on Friday after Lahore Police Chief &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;Umar Sheikh&lt;/font&gt;, the lead investigator of the case, rebuked the woman for driving down the motorway late at night without a man accompanying her.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Pakistani Authorities\' Reaction&amp;nbsp;: &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Condemning the brutal attack, Pakistani Prime Minister&amp;nbsp;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;Imran Khan&lt;/font&gt;&amp;nbsp;wrote in a statement on Twitter that he was closely following the case and had directed the investigators to arrest and sentence those involved in the incident &ldquo;as soon as possible&rdquo;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Khan added that his government would work towards strengthening laws to address the threat posed by a surge in rape cases involving women and children in recent years.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Earlier this year, Pakistani lawmakers had passed a bill, which called for the &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 231, 206);&quot;&gt;public hanging &lt;/font&gt;of all those convicted of the sexual abuse and murder of children.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;', '09:01:08 PM', 'Protest-in-Pakistan-after-gang-rape-of-woman-in-front-of-children-on-highway', '', 'https://indianexpress.com/article/pakistan/pakistan-gangrape-lahore-sialkot-protests-6593131/', 'Protest in Pakistan after gangraping woman in front of children on highway', '', 'Pakistan, Crime, Rape, Anger', 'Report'),
(34, 'Mask can slow spread & help build immunity?', 'Vinay', 'General', '2020-09-13', '&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;University of Cali&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;fornia :&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;University of California in San Francisco said face masks could work like variolation to generate immunity and&amp;nbsp;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 198, 156);&quot;&gt;slow the spread of Covid infection.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Before a vaccine for smallpox was discovered, people used to take recourse to variolation, a process in which those who didn&rsquo;t yet have the disease were exposed to material from the scabs of smallpox patients.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;According to experts, with a long-standing theory of viral pathogenesis, which holds that the severity of the disease is proportionate to the viral inoculum received.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;According to NEJM &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 198, 156);&quot;&gt;masks filter out some virus-containing droplets&lt;/font&gt;, masking might reduce the inoculum that an exposed person inhales.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Journal :&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;A study from the Journal of Hospital Infection found that wearing a face covering slashed the risk of infection by &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 198, 156);&quot;&gt;24% for a simple cotton covering&lt;/font&gt; and up to &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 198, 156);&quot;&gt;99% for a professional, medical-grade filtration mask.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Journal said that the most protective masks, N95 respirators, block 95% of tiny particles, including viruses, but during the pandemic they\'ve been hard to come by and organizations have said medical and health care workers should be given first dibs.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The earliest recommendations from the WHO supported the stance that healthy people didn\'t need to wear masks, but after more evidence emerged, the organization updated its official recommendation.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Some people suggest that medical masks (also known as surgical masks) &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 198, 156);&quot;&gt;trap exhaled carbon dioxide&lt;/font&gt; and cause you to breathe in more CO2.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;', '01:59:52 PM', 'Mask-can-slow-spread-help-build-immunity-', '', 'https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.cnet.com/google-amp/news/7-harmful-face-mask-myths-about-covid-19-you-dont-want-to-fall-for-or-spread/\r\nhttps://m.timesofindia.com/india/masks-can-help-build-immunity-journal/amp_articleshow/78084230.cms', 'Mask can slow spread and help build immunity', '', 'Health, Covid-19, Mask, WHO, University of California, precautions', 'Report'),
(35, 'Ex-CBI chiefâ€™s â€˜good riddanceâ€™ tweet on Swami Agnivesh death taken down by Twitter', 'Sumit', 'General', '2020-09-13', '&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot; color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;Twitter :&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Twitter has taken down former chief of CBI and retired IPS officer &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;M Nageswara Rao&rsquo;s &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;tweet in which he termed the death of social activist &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;Swami Agnivesh&lt;/font&gt; a &ldquo;good riddance&rdquo;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Twitter said the tweet violated its rules against abuse and harassment and has temporarily limited some of the account features.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Responding to his tweet on Agnivesh, Indian Police Foundation posted on Twitter&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&quot;Tweeting such hate messages&hellip;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 231, 206);&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;he has desecrated the police uniform and embarrassed the government.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt; He demoralises the entire police force&hellip;especially young officers.&quot;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;After repeated demands, Twitter decided to take down the tweets, stating that it violated the guidelines of the website.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Nageshwar Rao :&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;Nageshwar Rao&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt; tweeted on Friday night &quot;Good Radiance&quot; after Swami Agnivesh death and also said you did enormous damage to Hinduism.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Rao tweeted, &quot;You were an Anti-Hindu donning saffron clothes. &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 231, 206);&quot;&gt;I am ashamed that you were born as a Telugu Brahmin&lt;/font&gt;&hellip;Lion in sheep clothes. My grievance against Yamaraj is why did he wait this long!&rdquo;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Rao, a 1986-batch Telugu-native officer, was removed from his posting with the CBI last year and spent a brief tenure as General (DG) Fire Services, Civil Defence and Home Guard, before he stepped down and retired in July this year.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Rao doubled down, tweeting, &quot;Why do we celebrate as festivals, the days savages were dead? Because they\'re pests destroying society and their death is a cause for celebration. It was also to warn people not to patronise the bad.&quot;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;', '09:06:16 PM', 'Ex-CBI-chief-s-good-riddance-tweet-on-Swami-Agnivesh-death-taken-down-by-Twitter', '', 'https://www.thenewsminute.com/article/twitter-takes-down-ex-ips-officer-nageswara-raos-tweet-swami-agnivesh-132929\r\nhttps://indianexpress.com/article/india/nageswara-rao-good-riddance-tweet-on-swami-agnivesh-death-taken-down-by-twitter-6594074/', 'Ex CBI chief good riddance tweet on Swami Agnivesh death taken down by Twitter', '', 'India, CBI, Swami Agnivesh, Twitter', 'Report');
INSERT INTO `post` (`id`, `title`, `author`, `category`, `date`, `blog`, `upload_time`, `post_url`, `code`, `source`, `image_name`, `brief`, `tags`, `type`) VALUES
(9, 'Impact of Banning Chinese Apps', 'Navneet', 'International', '2020-08-07', '&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-93d80f2c-7fff-f0ed-c08e-9837ce94275e&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;After\r\nthe continuous face-offs with Chinese forces and a violent clash on June 15\r\n(causing casualties on both sides) , the Indian Government on June 29 banned &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;59 apps&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt; of Chinese origin.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Including some famous apps like TikTok\r\n, UC Browser, Shareit etc. The Ministry of Electronics and Information\r\nTechnology (MeitY), invoked Information Technology (IT) Act, 2000 to cite the\r\nconcerns regarding both data security and national sovereignty associated with\r\nthese apps.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 115%;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;In a\r\nfurther move, &lt;b&gt;47 more apps&lt;/b&gt; were\r\nbanned, which are said to be the clones of previously banned apps. This app\r\nwas highly anticipated by Indian software companies.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.9rem;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:18.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:18.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%&quot;&gt;How will it affect the users?&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;Installed apps may continue to exist on mobile\r\ndevices. But now that the latest versions of the apps have been removed from\r\nGoogle&rsquo;s Play Store and Apple&rsquo;s App Store, users will not be able to access\r\nupdated versions in future. If a notice goes out to internet service providers\r\nasking that data flow from these apps be halted, that could impact the\r\nfunctioning of existing, installed apps.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo6&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:18.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:18.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%&quot;&gt;How does the ban affect Chinese app providers?&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:18.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;The potential loss of advertising revenue impacts\r\napp-makers. Tik Tok&rsquo;s parent ByteDance Ltd. recorded a doubling of global\r\nrevenue to $17 billion in 2019, over the previous year, with $3 billion in\r\nprofit.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;Its India business may have yielded only $5.8 million\r\nin revenue for the year ended March 2019, but with quicker user adoption more\r\nrecently, the stakes seem to be getting higher. When TikTok was banned briefly\r\nin India last year on the grounds that it reportedly promoted pornography, the company had told a local court that it was losing roughly $15 million a month\r\ndue to the ban, according to a Reuters report.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo4&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:17.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:17.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%&quot;&gt;Merits of this Ban:&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:17.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;No Longer\r\nReliance on Passive Diplomacy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%&quot;&gt;: The decision to ban these apps, which comes amid continuing\r\ntensions between India and China is the clear message from India that it will\r\nno longer be a victim of China&rsquo;s Nibble and Negotiate policy and will review\r\nthe norms of engagement.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;Hurting Chinese\r\nAmbition&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;:\r\nThe ban may affect one of China&rsquo;s most ambitious goals, namely to become the digital superpower of the 21st century.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;Recognising\r\nImportance of Data&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%&quot;&gt;: India&rsquo;s app ban, and consideration of related restrictions on telecom\r\nhardware and mobile handsets is based on the recognition that data streams and\r\ndigital technology is a new currency of global power.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:18.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:18.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%&quot;&gt;Challenges &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:18.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo5&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;Data Privacy Issue Not Limited\r\nto Chinese Apps: MeitY banned apps on reports of stealing and transmitting\r\nusers data in an unauthorised manner to servers which have locations outside\r\nIndia.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo5&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;However, data privacy and\r\ndata security concerns are not limited only to Chinese apps.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo5&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;Damage Done Already: The apps\r\nthat were banned were very popular in India and the move to block them comes\r\nafter these apps had already amassed hundreds of millions of users in India.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo5&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;India&rsquo;s Economic Dependencies\r\non China: The ban on Chinese mobile apps is a relatively soft target, as India\r\nremains reliant on Chinese products in several critical and strategically\r\nsensitive sectors.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo5&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;From semiconductors and\r\nactive pharmaceutical ingredients to the telecom sector, Chinese vendors are\r\ninvolved not only in India&rsquo;s 4G network but in on-going 5G trials as well.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;Also, Chinese finance is\r\npresently essential to sustaining India&rsquo;s start-up economy. As many Indian\r\nUnicorns such as Paytm, Zomato, Byju&rsquo;s are having Chinese shareholders.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo7&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:18.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;â—&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:18.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%&quot;&gt;Looking Forward&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:18.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;Weeding Out Obsolete Legislations&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;: India&rsquo;s digital\r\napplications are governed by obsolete laws, which is unsuitable in the context\r\nof today&rsquo;s digital scenario.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;Information\r\nTechnology Act, 2000 (20-year-old law) was designed for the business process\r\noutsourcing ecosystem, not for modern digital applications or platforms.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;Similarly,\r\nthe Copyright Act, which provides incentives and protections for most of the\r\ncontent that sits at the heart of the digital economy, was last amended in\r\n2012. Thus, there is a strong case to revise the key legislations and syncing\r\nthem to change the digital environment.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;Need For A Data Protection Law&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;: Data privacy and security\r\nremains to be major challenges emanating from the ongoing digital revolution.\r\nThus, a data protection law is long overdue.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot; style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt